# Goal
geometry_msgs/Point target_frontier  # Target frontier to explore
float32 timeout  # Exploration timeout in seconds
---
# Feedback
float32 progress  # Exploration progress (0.0-1.0)
geometry_msgs/Point current_position  # Current robot position
string status_message  # Status message
---
# Result
bool success  # Whether exploration was successful
string message  # Result message
geometry_msgs/Point final_position  # Final robot position